<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="KC1">
<l>kaṇṇi nuṉciṟut tāmpiṉāl kaṭṭu uṇṇap</l>
<l>paṇṇiya perumāyaṉ eṉ appaṉil</l>
<l>naṇṇit teṉkurukūr nampi eṉṟakkāl</l>
<l>aṇṇikkum amutu ūṟum eṉ nāvukkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even more than my Father, Peṟumāyaṉ, who made [himself]</l>
<l rend="indent">	agreeable to being bound with the thin, small rope of a noose,</l>
<l>having approached [Caṭakōpaṉ], at the time that [I] say,</l>
<l rend="inent">“Lord of southern Kurukūr,”</l>
<l>my tongue waters [with] sweet tasting nectar.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
